<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <style>
 	.box1 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(red, yellow);
    }
    
    .box2 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, red, yellow);
    }
    
    .box3 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, red, yellow);
    }
    
    .box4 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(to top right, red, yellow);
    }
    
    .box5 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, red, yellow, red, yellow);
    }
    
    .box6 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, red 10px, yellow 30px, red 50px, yellow);
    }
    
    .box7 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 160px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, red 0%, red 25%, yellow 25%, yellow 50%, red 50%, red 75%, yellow 75%);
    }
        
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <pre>
    linear-gradient([&lt;angle> | to &lt;side-or-corner>]? , &lt;color-stop-list>)
    
    这个函数（特性）接受的第一个参数是渐变的角度，他可以接受一个表示角度的值（可用的单位deg、rad、grad或turn）
    或者是表示方向的关键词（top、right、bottom、left、left top、top right、bottom right或者left bottom）。
    
    第二个参数是接受一系列颜色节点（终止点的颜色）。
  </pre>
  
  <span>默认是to bottom，也就是180deg<span>
  <div class="box1"></div>
    
  <span>使用to top<span>
  <div class="box2"></div>
    
  <span>使用0deg，效果和to top一样<span>
  <div class="box3"></div>
    
  <span>使用to top right<span>
  <div class="box4"></div>
    
  <span>多渐变色<span>
  <div class="box5"></div>

  <span>渐变宽度<span>
  <div class="box6"></div>
    
  <span>渐变宽度<span>
  <div class="box7"></div>
</body>
</html>
